            "pc_requirements": {
                "minimum": "<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> 64bit Windows 7 SP1 / Windows 8 / Windows 8.1 / Windows 10<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> 2.3+ GHz<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 4 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> DX11 with Feature Level 10.1, SM4<br></li><li><strong>DirectX:</strong> Version 11<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 16 GB available space<br></li><li><strong>Additional Notes:</strong> Make sure your drivers and Windows are updated. Supported chipsets: NVIDIA 470 GTX, AMD HD6850, Intel HD4600 or greater. Laptop versions of these chipsets may not be supported. Updates to your video and sound card drivers may be required. We'll be constantly updating the game to lower the required specs, so bear with us if your machine is struggling.</li></ul>",
                "recommended": "<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> 64bit Windows 7 SP1/ Windows 8 / Windows 8.1 / Windows 10<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> 3.40 GHz<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 8 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> DX11 with Feature Level 11, SM5<br></li><li><strong>DirectX:</strong> Version 11<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 16 GB available space<br></li><li><strong>Additional Notes:</strong> Make sure your drivers and Windows are updated. Supported chipsets: NVIDIA 570 GTX, AMD HD7850, Intel Iris or greater. Laptop versions of these chipsets may not be supported. Updates to your video and sound card drivers may be required. We'll be constantly updating the game to lower the required specs, so bear with us if your machine is struggling.</li></ul>"
